item.title: Random Kazan
item.description: Random Kazan # Temple of All Religions / Universal Temple # Architect - Ildar Khanov The house of Kazan artist Ildar Khanov is an original building that unites in a complex of world religions, next to a mosque, a church, a Buddhist pagoda, and a Synagogue, the domes of religions of disappeared civilisations are being built.
